Replaces: iridium-codecs-ffmpeg-dbg
Description: iridium-codecs-ffmpeg-extra debug symbols
 Debug symbols for the extra ffmpeg-mt codecs

Package: iridium-chromedriver
Architecture: armhf armel i386 amd64
Pre-Depends: dpkg (>= 1.15.6)
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, iridium-browser (>= 4.0.203.0~)
Description: WebDriver driver for the Iridium Browser
 Chromedriver serves as a bridge between Iridium Browser and Selenium 
 WebDriver.
 .
 See http://code.google.com/p/selenium/wiki/ChromeDriver for details.

